<item>
            <title>[LU-4811] Interop 2.5&lt;-&gt;2.6 failure on test suite sanity test_24u: error on ioctl 0x4008669a, no data availiable</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4811</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/acaf508a-b240-11e3-a93f-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/acaf508a-b240-11e3-a93f-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_24u failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;error() without useful message, please fix&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 24u: create stripe file == 12:37:21 (1395430641)
error on ioctl 0x4008669a for &apos;/mnt/lustre/f24u.sanity&apos; (3): No data available
write: Bad file descriptor
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>server: 2.5.1&lt;br/&gt;
client: lustre-master build # 1945</environment>
        <key id="23858">LU-4811</key>
            <summary>Interop 2.5&lt;-&gt;2.6 failure on test suite sanity test_24u: error on ioctl 0x4008669a, no data availiable</summary>
